Package: ecoflex
Title: Flexible Econometric Models for Applied Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Diletta", "Abbonato", email = "diletta.abbonato@unito.it",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements econometric models for applied microeconomics and
    causal inference. Covers hurdle models with arbitrary thresholds,
    Heckman selection models, regression discontinuity designs, IV/GMM
    estimation, difference-in-differences for staggered adoption, Tobit
    types I-V, nonlinear panel models, and switching regressions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
